locality: Entre Tuléar et St-Augustin. Plateau calcaire.
Reserve de Tsimanampetsotsa; NW corner of Reserve.

Ngorongoro Conservation Area. West of Endulen airstrip. Savanna woodland dominated by Acacia hockii. Informants: Naitipa Metele grandmother c. 55 years, Lekura and Kidami Metele, Irmakaa age group and Peter Metele Irkingónde-age group, c.30 years.
Forest along road to Morombe 16-18 km N of Tulear; near sea level.
